description.en: Evermusk is a hyper-deflationary token on the Binance Smart Chain. 7% of all transactions are given the friendly whale to buy back automatically through Pancake Swap! Coins that he buys are then burned! You will never see 2 sales in a row. This is how we are programmed to moon, it is in the code. Join us as we aim to give power to the community by giving back while being as transparent as possible. Buckle up if you know where we are heading! This is one token you would regret missing out on!!
